trans-unit.source: Provides access to add attributes for one specific type to one specific <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Zapewnia dostęp do dodania atrybuty dla określonego typu jeden do jednego określonego <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The first time an <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> is queried for attributes for a type, if the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> was populated using <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A> for that type, the delegate is passed a AttributeCallbackBuilder.
trans-unit.target: Po raz pierwszy <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>jest poddawany kwerendzie dla atrybutów dla typu, jeśli <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder>został wypełniony przy użyciu <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>dla tego typu obiektu delegowanego jest przekazywany AttributeCallbackBuilder.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> removes the callback reference and adds any attribute information provided by calls to <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>Usuwa odwołanie do wywołania zwrotnego i dodaje wszystkie informacje o atrybutach podał wywołań <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>

trans-unit.source: Adds the contents of the provided attributes to the attribute table that created this builder.
trans-unit.target: Dodaje zawartość podane atrybuty do tabeli atrybutów utworzony tego konstruktora.

trans-unit.source: If an attribute conflicts with another attribute already included in the table, the last attribute added replaces previous attributes.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli atrybut jest w konflikcie z innym atrybucie już uwzględniony w tabeli, ostatniego atrybutu dodane zastępuje poprzednie atrybuty.

trans-unit.source: Attributes can be added only to the type specified by <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Atrybuty można dodać tylko do typu określonego przez <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The attributes that are added to the table.
trans-unit.target: Atrybuty, które są dodawane do tabeli.
